precept ComputedTaxNet

# Demonstrates computed-field intermediary proofs across derived values.
# The proof engine keeps Tax non-negative and Net strictly positive once
# Subtotal stays positive and TaxRate remains between 0 and 0.99.

field Subtotal as number default 120 positive
field TaxRate as number default 0.08 min 0 max 0.99

field Tax as number -> Subtotal * TaxRate nonnegative
field Net as number -> Subtotal - Tax positive

edit Subtotal, TaxRate
